---
title: Chicken Schnitzel with Roasted Veggies & Creamy Mustard Sauce
description: Coat pork in breadcrumbs and immediately become a mealtime MVP. Crispy pork is pretty much perfect in any form, but this isn’t your run-of-the-mill schnitzel. To amp up flavor, we’ve added lemon zest and garlic powder to our breadcrumb mixture, then drizzled the crispy pork chops with our new favorite condiment: creamy honey mustard sauce. Speaking of, we’re serving up sides of roasted potatoes and broccoli for extra dipping, but if you broke out the spoon to scrape up leftover sauce, we wouldn’t judge.
